This paper is likely to belong to cs.SD (Sound) as it deals with speaker adaptation in automatic speech recognition. It may also belong to cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it involves deep neural networks and classification. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves adversarial learning and optimization. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.SI (Signal Processing) as it deals with processing speech signals.
